# NetworkStatusLogger - HTTP Response Monitor

NetworkStatusLogger checks multiple URLs and logs their availability, response time, and error rates.

## Features
- Configurable timeout  
- CSV logging  
- Color-coded output  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/25_NetworkStatusLogger.git
cd 25_NetworkStatusLogger
python monitor.py
